HB 981 Original 2026 Regular Session Villio
Abstract: Extends the termination date for the Law Enforcement Recruitment Incentive
Program.
Present law establishes the Law Enforcement Recruitment Incentive Program to aid in the
recruitment of law enforcement officers in the state. Establishes the Law Enforcement
Recruitment Incentive Fund to fund the program.
Proposed law changes the termination date of the program from July 1, 2027, to July 1,
2029.
(Amends R.S. 40:1669(J))
